Creating an LWC Card Layout
Create a new LWC card layout to enable Vlocity Lightning web components.

Beginning with the Vlocity Insurance and Health Summer '19 and Vlocity Communications, Media, and Energy Fall '19 releases, Vlocity supports the Salesforce Lightning Web Component programming model.

To create a new LWC Card Layout:
LWC Enable an Angular Card Layout
Allow an Angular card to work with Lightning web components.
Remote Site URL Configuration
Ensure that you configured the remote site URL correctly.
Lightning Web Component Settings Configuration
Ensure that you configured Lightning Web component settings correctly.
title: Vlocity Lightning Web Components and OmniStudio
